headline: What the Kimmel Show Controversy Could Mean for Two Local TV Station Stocks
summary: President Trump said Thursday that broadcasters that are mostly critical of him should have their licenses revoked.

headline: Paramount and WBD, UPS, Apple iPhone 17: Trending Tickers
summary: Market Catalysts host Julie Hyman tracks several of the day's top trending stock tickers, including the latest news on Paramount Skydance's (PSKY) acquisition bid for Warner Bros. Discovery (WBD), United Parcel Service (UPS) receiving a downgrade, and the Apple (AAPL) iPhone 17 and iPhone Air hitting store shelves today.
